  "title": "Healthcare Assistant/Care Support Associate  #HJO",
  "description": "<p></p><p><strong>Job Description:</strong></p><ul><li>Assist patients with daily living activities (ADLs) such as bathing, feeding, and diaper changes.</li><li>Take and record vital signs accurately, maintaining proper documentation.</li><li>Provide general assistance to ensure patients’ comfort, hygiene, and safety.</li><li>Other ad hoc duties</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum GCE ‘N’ / ‘O’ Levels</li><li>Able to commence work immediately / short notice</li><li></li></ul><p>Interested candidates are invited to email your resume to:</p><p></p><p>jen.ooi@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>Jenalyn Ooi Huai Sian (R1765551)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  | Company Reg. No. 199601303W | EA License Number: 99C4599</p><p></p>",
